<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In the practical use and application of the standard gauge esablished <ref class="footnoteRef" idref="fn002140">1</ref><note type="footnote" id="fn002140"><num>1</num> So in original. Probably should be “established”.</note> in <ref href="/us/usc/t15/s206">section 206 of this title</ref> a variation of 2½ percent, either way may be allowed.</p>
